
'''= connect Wikipedia articles with places'''

URL = http://www.placeopedia.com/

=Description=

"a simple site where you can connect Wikipedia articles with places, and then make use of our database either to browse, or syndicate the whole lot. We hope that lots of people will connect places they know with their corresponding Wikipedia article, and then our syndicated data can be used as a general geographic lookup table for Wikipedia."


